text: Arnold Zdebiak (born 11 May 1993) is a Polish bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Poland Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:People from Żary County
